00:37:23.220 --> 00:37:24.610
school in the US.

00:37:24.610 --> 00:37:27.280
And I think there are two
reasons why I wrote the book.

00:37:27.280 --> 00:37:29.140
One is because I find this
stuff intrinsically

00:37:29.140 --> 00:37:30.140
fascinating.

00:37:30.140 --> 00:37:32.610
And I think other people
tend to when I

00:37:32.610 --> 00:37:33.430
discuss it with them.

00:37:33.430 --> 00:37:34.920
And so I thought there
