00:37:36.680 --> 00:37:39.710
But I also think, if you look
at the hurricane example,

00:37:39.710 --> 00:37:41.520
there's good reason
to talk about this

00:37:41.520 --> 00:37:43.000
stuff for policy reasons.

00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:45.570
Why shouldn't we name our
