00:37:45.570 --> 00:37:45.970
differently?

00:37:45.970 --> 00:37:47.520
It costs us nothing.

00:37:47.520 --> 00:37:50.110
And in so doing, we might
attract more hurricane aid.

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:51.850
It just seems like
a no brainer.

00:37:51.850 --> 00:37:54.180
So if we can capitalize on this
stuff, there are no side

00:37:54.180 --> 00:37:57.070
effects to renaming our
hurricanes, really.

00:37:57.070 --> 00:37:58.620
Some of the effects are great.

00:37:58.620 --> 00:38:00.660
And so from a policy
perspective, there's a lot we

00:38:00.660 --> 00:38:02.370
can do that we aren't doing.

00:38:02.370 --> 00:38:04.570
And this book talks about
some of those effects.

00:38:04.570 --> 00:38:07.130
So I think it's interesting and
because it has practical

00:38:07.130 --> 00:38:08.380
consequences.

